situation of human rights and fundamental freedoms of indigenous people thanked Mr. Cooney 
from the Asian Development Bank for his willingness to continue the dialogue on the potential 
impact of the construction of Nam Theun 2 dam on the human rights, including the right to food, 
of the affected communities and for the additional information that was sent to the Special 
